{"tid":578094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港啲細路無得救","createTime":"2018-03-02T10:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T04:55:53.000Z","uid":104046,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3c0b411766225de576e8f0f35ff280db69c3eca6","tid":578094,"uid":104046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/175414_2c52387838664ae07dda8754e7d4f5e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F175414_2c52387838664ae07dda8754e7d4f5e4.png&h=3532aa0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人地唔記得落車，落唔到車，個細路就話人抵死抵死，仲要同對面阿嫲講人地唔記得落車，嗰大嘅又唔出聲教佢。人地想係大水坑落講到去石門，一見有位坐就尻衝過去，一啲家教都無。依家啲細路一啲禮貌都無，哥哥姐姐唔識叫，叫呢個嗰個，唔該都無聲。<br />\n<br />\n依家啲細路咁樣，香港仲得了嘅！"},{"pid":"e7f99b59d4622caf5a56dbc43a02e31d698642b3","tid":578094,"uid":10844,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:06:05.000Z","msg":"你影佢相都冇用㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一就臨閂門前一手掉佢出車"},{"pid":"53e1d9db83b73a68782f7b4babd0105ef58bb854","tid":578094,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:06:17.000Z","msg":"醒少少記得落車咪唔洗比人笑囉樓主"},{"pid":"2f91e50313e4b9b15c0f7a63281268965c1d9a83","tid":578094,"uid":15659,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"一個細路咁你就講到全港啲細路都冇家教，似乎係你冇得救多啲"},{"pid":"ebd0142b22f43527434e1a0cdd2ec5b924b14c00","tid":578094,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"係我就行埋去 「的」起個細路，鬧佢無家教"},{"pid":"1360c7226dbe59d609d709ef2897fdec4eae949e","tid":578094,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:12:27.000Z","msg":"我聽日放假"},{"pid":"52b3b73883f646f707f2470ad95602f4a7a05801","tid":578094,"uid":174074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"On9細路 冇眼睇"},{"pid":"774c48729d855